    <p>e-Pets’ Day Out: Happy Pets, Happy Peo­ple</p>
    <p>Hosted on the Na­tional Parks Board’s An­i­malBuz­zSG Face­book page, the third dig­i­tal Pets’ Day Out fea­tures live chat seg­ments in which vets will an­swer ques­tions on re­spon­si­ble pet own­er­ship and give ba­sic dog train­ing tips. For Pro­ject Adore, a re­hom­ing pro­gramme for mid-sized mixed-breed dogs in Hous­ing Board flats, an­i­mal wel­fare groups and adopters will share their sto­ries on giv­ing these dogs a sec­ond chance.</p>


